  "narrative": {
    "text": "Indonesia is a East Asia and Pacific country with a DB-type pension system centred on the Jaminan Pensiun (JP) \u2013 BPJS Ketenagakerjaan Old-Age Pension (DB). The system includes 2 schemes: Jaminan Pensiun (JP) \u2013 BPJS Ketenagakerjaan Old-Age Pension (DB), Jaminan Hari Tua (JHT) \u2013 BPJS Ketenagakerjaan Provident Fund (DC). The normal retirement age is 65 for both men and women. Contributions total 5.0% of insurable earnings (3.0% employee, 2.0% employer).",
